{"tid":1679611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「行動」一句講晒，10.31晚去太子定去老蘭？","createTime":"2019-10-28T09:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T16:24:48.000Z","uid":82452,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4fa4dc6f4eea0f731e1325777c21957e300769","tid":1679611,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:56:16.000Z","msg":"屌你！！仲駛諗？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋全部同我去太子呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去太子係咪唔戴得面具呀？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得哎嘛！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831已經兩個月喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾多手足受傷同被捕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰一晚到底打死幾多人都未查清楚呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQdaqyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQdaqyZ.jpg&h=b2bfd1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yddJLy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyddJLy0.jpg&h=9d359fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2FHgFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2FHgFG.jpg&h=18d1f547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtfTokH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtfTokH.jpg&h=2f582bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月31號<br />\n七點要人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太子狗屋外</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去到有咩做？<br />\n<br />\n去深水埗買完面具再去花墟買紮花<br />\n然後一齊獻花、上香、鞠躬、鳩企咩都好<br />\n我要10月31號晚係太子見到你哋！！！<br />\n<br />\n毋忘8.31！<br />\n香港人！反抗！"},{"pid":"ec5129260aa92077d761af1a9108fa19a0616149","tid":1679611,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cbd35affa2bc3251aee15634fa8d4e43200c7f2d","tid":1679611,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD59ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=4ddaa444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"7eddbdc1e6d90279e32f1e6c0f563c84dbe9102c","tid":1679611,"uid":272292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99b00b93d4cbf95f18a86caf96b969877d0fc325","tid":1679611,"uid":264609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uK89F9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuK89F9F.jpg&h=def0b89f&s={SIZE}\" />推"},{"pid":"d4d36ad90f6cc3658e6c9b119e83587e1ffe0ad3","tid":1679611,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0082ec4ebc9c81fb5f6da5ba78726e4dca28c45","tid":1679611,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"到時太子站+前後港䥫站定必封站"},{"pid":"cb7ea4e0b9088582b2d71562cbc842c7eba0208b","tid":1679611,"uid":14070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass